It’s never enough 📸 Share if you agree 😅
As a content creator, there’s no such thing as too much gear! That ‘what if’ moment always gets us, making us carry every single piece of gear —even for the simplest shoot. 🎥📸😂

Must say, people from Kerala are so kind and helpful ☺️
